I will keep you safe.

37
00:02:15,170 --> 00:02:16,890
I'll listen to everything you say, Lengbei.

38
00:02:22,220 --> 00:02:25,010
Is there something else troubling you?

39
00:02:30,130 --> 00:02:31,130
There are things

40
