I didn't want to involve you,

41
00:02:36,060 --> 00:02:37,060
but...

42
00:02:37,730 --> 00:02:39,730
I am your closest kin in this world.

43
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:42,220
If there's anything you need from me,

44
