82
00:05:38,620 --> 00:05:40,220
But they're unlikely to return.

83
00:05:44,410 --> 00:05:45,660
After all, things have changed.

84
00:05:48,170 --> 00:05:49,660
Things have changed...

85
00:05:57,740 --> 00:05:58,860
But

86
00:06:00,620 --> 00:06:02,420
